{
  "stem": "18778.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was always my dream that someday I would take my children back to my hometown and to the house where I was raised and to show them their roots.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it became a reality in 1979.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think it was-- or was it-- No.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was 1975.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm sorry. 1975.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think both children were still in college.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Joani was two years ahead of Joel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, it was arranged so that the two of them would have a taste of Europe by themselves by going to England for a week together.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we then met up with them in Germany.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Meanwhile.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My husband has two-- had two brothers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And each brother had one of his children along.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we all met eventually in their hometown of Andernach.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We stayed in a small hotel right on the Rhine embankment.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we kind of took over a whole floor of the hotel.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Also, my-- my nanny joined us there with her husband.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we visited the home where my husband was born and raised.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And that house, by the way, had a date on it from the 1600s.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was a very old house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And Andernach was a very old town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's near Koblenz.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's on the Rhine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was founded by the Romans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, they had their thousandth anniversary a few years ago, the town of Andernach.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there were Jews there already I think in the 10th century.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] After-- after meeting in Andernach, I took my children to Rheydt.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But this time, I didn't do what I did the last time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I had written to the owner of the house.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
